{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-453-lattice-quadrilaterals","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Zadatak 453: Četvorougaonik koordinata","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Jednostavan četvorugon je četvorugon koji ima četiri različite tačke, nema pravougaone uglove i nije oštećen sam po sebi.</p>\n<p>Neka je $Q(m, n)$ broj jednostavnih četvorougličnika čije su tačke rešetkaste tačke sa koordinatama ($x$, $y$) koje zadovoljavaju $0 ≤ x ≤ m$ i $0 ≤ y ≤ n$.</p>\n<p>Na primer, $Q(2, 2) = 94$ kao što je prikazano ispod:</p>\n<img alt=\"94 quadrilaterals whose vertices are lattice points with coordinates (x, y) satiffying 0 &le; x &le; m and 0 &le; y &le; n\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/lattice-quadrilaterals.png\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Može se dokazati da $Q(3, 7) = 39\\,590$, $Q(12, 3) = 309\\,000$ i $Q(123, 45) = 70\\,542\\,215\\,894\\,646$.</p>\n<p>Izračunaj $Q(12\\,345, 6\\,789)\\bmod 135\\,707\\,531$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f5311000cf542c510044","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302126,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-453-lattice-quadrilaterals"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function latticeQuadrilaterals() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nlatticeQuadrilaterals();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>latticeQuadrilaterals()</